      ],
      "source": "https://delawareriverheritagetrail.org/2021/09/28/borough-of-palmyra/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The town began as a small railroad junction called Texas, named after the 1845 U.S. territory that joined the Union.",
